      "test fires: ['August_Complex', 'Beckwourth_Complex', 'CZU_Lightning_Complex', 'Dolan', 'LNU_Lightning_Complex', 'McCash', 'Walker', 'Windy']\n",
      "hours used total: 22230\n",
